        "content": "# VECTOR INDEXING\n\n- Creates embeddings for KB chunks.\n- Stores chunk vectors in the Pinecone KB namespace.\n- Namespace is set upstream in `Prepare Chunk Metadata` and read by Pinecone as `={{ $json.namespace || 'SpaceKonceptRental_kb' }}`.\n\n## Required manual configuration:\n\n- **Insert Chunks into Pinecone**\n  - `pineconeIndex`: Set this to the Pinecone index used for vector storage.",
