      "parameters": {
        "content": "# INGESTION LOG\n\n- Records ingestion status for review.\n- Groups Pinecone chunk outputs back into one log row per source file.\n- Upserts by `file_id`, so repeated events update the existing row while new files keep appending.\n- Writes file names as plain text and Drive URLs as clickable links in Sheets.\n\n## Required manual configuration:\n\n- **Append KB Ingestion Log**\n  - `documentId.value`: Set this to the Google Sheets workbook used for ingestion logs.\n  - Sheet headers must include `file_url` and `event_type` if those columns are used.",
